He hit you?
Knocked me out.

28:18.064 --> 28:20.266
He's been gone
at least half an hour.

28:20.298 --> 28:21.700
Any idea where he's headed?

28:27.973 --> 28:30.409
* Oh, Mario

28:30.442 --> 28:33.612
* Sit here by the window

28:33.644 --> 28:35.247
One of them
take your wallet?

28:38.084 --> 28:39.885
What's that?

28:39.919 --> 28:43.288
The way you're scanning
that crowd, you look like
you're out for blood.

28:43.322 --> 28:46.724
I'm just lookin'
for a certain bird
I met here the other night.

28:47.726 --> 28:48.594
Oh.

28:51.163 --> 28:54.299
Is it me?
Sorry, luv.
Don't think so.

28:56.301 --> 28:58.336
Not even if I ask nice?

29:02.407 --> 29:05.176
Or are you the type
that has to be convinced?

29:07.078 --> 29:10.648
Friendly warning, pet.
I'm the type best left alone.

29:10.682 --> 29:13.652
Oh, I get it.

29:13.684 --> 29:16.955
You'd rather I slip into
something more comfortable.

29:21.326 --> 29:23.895
Should we pick off
the crowd one by one...

29:23.930 --> 29:26.332
or block the exits
and ravish the place?

29:26.365 --> 29:29.935
Get away from me.
What's with
the wallflower act?

29:29.969 --> 29:33.471
You didn't seem so shy
when you were... biting me.

29:35.875 --> 29:37.542
I'm not asking if you
want to be soul mates.

29:39.211 --> 29:41.646
Just... figured you'd
wanna have some fun.

29:43.281 --> 29:46.785
Mmm.
I take him. You take her.

29:48.153 --> 29:49.955
Or the other way around.
Whatever.

29:49.989 --> 29:51.690
No, you're lying!

29:56.162 --> 29:58.830
So that all I was to you,
a one-bite stand?

29:58.865 --> 30:01.633
* Because nobody knows

30:01.666 --> 30:04.369
* That's how I nearly fell

30:04.403 --> 30:07.605
* Trading clothes

30:07.638 --> 30:10.608
* And ringing Pavlov's bell

30:10.642 --> 30:13.278
* History shows

30:13.311 --> 30:17.083
* But rarely shows it well

30:18.584 --> 30:20.419
* Well, well, well

30:42.340 --> 30:46.311
* Because nobody knows

30:46.345 --> 30:49.882
* That's how I nearly fell

30:49.915 --> 30:52.750
* Trading clothes

30:52.784 --> 30:54.752
* And ringing Pavlov's bell

30:54.786 --> 30:55.887
(music stops)

31:04.130 --> 31:07.333
* History shows

31:07.365 --> 31:11.037
* But rarely shows it well

31:15.974 --> 31:18.743
Hey, sweetheart,
if you want to go in,
go ahead.

31:18.777 --> 31:22.347
Uh, actually,
I need some help.
I-I'm looking for this guy.

31:22.381 --> 31:25.616
Bleached blond hair,
leather jacket,
British accent, kind of...

31:25.651 --> 31:27.953
sallow but in a hot way?

31:27.987 --> 31:30.388
Yeah, yeah.
I know the guy.
Billy Idol wannabe?

31:30.422 --> 31:33.224
Actually, Billy Idol
stole his look from--

31:33.259 --> 31:35.527
Never mind.
Has he been here?

31:35.560 --> 31:37.262
This guy your boyfriend
or somethin'?

31:38.564 --> 31:41.968
No. I just--
I need to find him
as soon as possible.

31:42.969 --> 31:45.203
Yeah, he comes in here
a lot lately.

31:45.237 --> 31:47.973
Every night leaves
with a different girl.
Chicks like Billy Idol.

31:50.108 --> 31:51.343
How many girls?

31:52.644 --> 31:55.913
Look, this guy that's
not your boyfriend guy?

31:55.948 --> 31:58.817
If I were you,
I'd lose him.
He's a real player.

32:09.028 --> 32:11.596
Man, I hate playing
vampire towns.

32:19.805 --> 32:21.640
Hello? It's me.

32:24.309 --> 32:25.676
I'm seein'--

32:26.877 --> 32:28.213
I think I'm remembering.

32:29.815 --> 32:32.018
I think I've done
some very bad things.

32:32.050 --> 32:35.586
Where are you?
I need--

32:35.621 --> 32:37.923
I need to see you.

32:37.955 --> 32:40.358
There's a house.
634 Hoffman Terrace.

32:40.392 --> 32:41.492
I'll meet you.

32:45.797 --> 32:47.865
You shouldn't have
done that.

32:47.898 --> 32:50.368
It's not time yet.
(chuckles)

32:50.402 --> 32:53.904
Not nearly. You're goin'
against the plan.

32:55.807 --> 32:57.308
But we can make it work.

33:13.224 --> 33:14.559
Down here.

33:25.537 --> 33:26.771
You won't come down?

33:29.075 --> 33:30.675
I understand.

33:32.077 --> 33:33.444
It's a risky proposition.

33:34.846 --> 33:38.683
There's an order.
The Slayer's not in order.

33:38.717 --> 33:42.320
But it can't hurt to play.
Get your claws in the mouse,
you know?

33:42.354 --> 33:44.256
You are not here.

33:54.432 --> 33:57.202
All right, what do you
want to show me?

33:58.604 --> 33:59.904
I've been remembering.

34:01.606 --> 34:04.076
It's the girl.
I walked her home.

34:05.443 --> 34:06.644
The one you saw.

34:08.246 --> 34:09.614
And the one before that.

34:11.949 --> 34:13.952
And I think I killed her.

34:14.985 --> 34:17.956
And I think I--
I think I killed...

34:17.989 --> 34:20.159
the lady who lived here.

34:21.159 --> 34:22.728
And...

34:22.760 --> 34:24.596
And there might be others.

34:27.431 --> 34:29.268
Oh, my God.

34:30.302 --> 34:31.469
Here.

34:36.074 --> 34:38.309
I-- I think
I buried them here.

34:41.480 --> 34:44.047
Spike, why?

34:44.081 --> 34:47.318
Well, I don't know, do I?
I don't even know how.

34:47.353 --> 34:49.887
I shouldn't be able--
 * Early one morning

34:49.920 --> 34:52.590
* Just as the sun was risin'

34:52.623 --> 34:57.163
* I heard a fair maid singing
in the valley down below *

34:57.195 --> 35:00.298
* Oh, don't deceive me
What? What is it?

35:00.331 --> 35:03.101
* Oh, never leave me

35:03.135 --> 35:07.306
* How could you use
a poor maid so *
Spike!

35:14.045 --> 35:15.746
What are you doing?

35:15.780 --> 35:17.148
Aaah!

35:20.518 --> 35:23.021
Spike, listen to me.
You don't wanna do this.

35:24.222 --> 35:26.824
And it's just about
to get fun.

35:34.500 --> 35:37.335
Oh, God.
(growling)

35:50.548 --> 35:52.818
You know what
I want you to do.

36:04.563 --> 36:06.532
They're waiting for you.

36:06.565 --> 36:09.400
Take her.
Taste her.
Make her weak.

36:12.938 --> 36:14.706
Spike! No!

36:18.443 --> 36:20.110
(growling)

36:48.706 --> 36:49.875
I remember.

37:16.467 --> 37:18.068
You've failed them.

37:19.838 --> 37:21.972
Now she's gonna kill you.

37:22.007 --> 37:24.242
You lose, mate.

37:28.914 --> 37:31.148
Sorry, ma'am.
But it's my job.
(coughing)

38:07.552 --> 38:09.286
Do it fast, okay?

38:12.324 --> 38:14.860
He said you would do it.

38:14.893 --> 38:16.161
Who said?

38:18.496 --> 38:19.530
Me.

38:21.733 --> 38:23.168
It was me.

38:24.869 --> 38:26.036
I saw it.

38:27.539 --> 38:31.309
I was here the whole time,
talkin' and singin'.

38:33.478 --> 38:34.913
There was this song.

38:36.681 --> 38:40.518
What are you talking about?
I don't know!

38:40.552 --> 38:43.153
Please, I don't remember.

38:43.188 --> 38:45.023
Don't make me remember.

38:47.257 --> 38:49.193
Make it so I forget again!

38:49.226 --> 38:51.195
I did what you wanted!

38:53.898 --> 38:55.567
There's something here.

39:02.039 --> 39:05.043
Oh, God. No, please,
I need that.

39:06.777 --> 39:09.715
I can't cry this soul
out of me.

39:09.748 --> 39:11.115
It won't come.

39:12.250 --> 39:15.219
I've killed,
and I can feel 'em.

39:16.788 --> 39:18.523
I can feel
every one of 'em.

39:28.233 --> 39:30.034
There's something
playing with us.

39:31.637 --> 39:33.271
All of us.

39:39.077 --> 39:40.445
What is it?

39:41.579 --> 39:43.047
Why is it
doin' this to me?

39:45.451 --> 39:47.284
I don't know.

39:50.422 --> 39:54.259
Will you... help me?

39:57.929 --> 39:59.797
Can you help me?

40:03.268 --> 40:04.570
BUFFY: I'll help you.

40:10.175 --> 40:11.476
ANYA:
And you believe him?

40:12.643 --> 40:14.713
BUFFY:
You didn't see him
down there.

40:14.746 --> 40:16.514
He really didn't know
what he'd done.

40:17.748 --> 40:19.985
It wasn't in his control.

40:20.018 --> 40:22.653
Oh, an out-of-control
serial killer.

40:22.688 --> 40:24.922
You're right. That is
a great house guest.

40:24.956 --> 40:26.791
Wait. Is he--

40:26.824 --> 40:30.161
Is he staying here?
I don't know.

40:30.195 --> 40:32.764
But I'm not letting him
out of my sight,
that's for sure.

40:32.797 --> 40:36.467
Buffy, he's been feeding--
on human blood.
That's gotta do stuff.

40:36.501 --> 40:39.369
I'm not keeping him around
just to help him.

40:40.438 --> 40:42.407
I think there was
something there

40:42.440 --> 40:44.309
talking to him,
making him do things.

40:44.342 --> 40:47.311
Something like what was
talking to us?

40:47.344 --> 40:49.414
Maybe.

40:49.447 --> 40:51.315
And if it was, then it's
been screwin' with Spike
big-time.

40:52.818 --> 40:55.085
So, you want him
around because...

40:55.119 --> 40:57.623
Look, there's
something evil working us,

40:57.655 --> 40:59.356
and if we are ever gonna have
a chance to fight it,

40:59.389 --> 41:01.358
we need to learn
everything we can about it.

41:01.391 --> 41:04.362
This thing has been
closer to Spike
than any of us.

41:05.396 --> 41:07.666
And if you want
to understand it...

41:08.699 --> 41:10.367
I'm gonna have to
get close to Spike.

41:10.400 --> 41:12.938
Nah, it's too dangerous.
BUFFY:
I don't have a choice.

41:12.971 --> 41:16.807
Whatever this thing is,
from beneath us, it's bad.

41:18.677 --> 41:20.144
And it's only getting worse.

41:30.420 --> 41:32.157
Oh, dear God!

41:35.492 --> 41:37.596
Robson, are you here?

41:39.831 --> 41:41.199
Robson!

41:41.231 --> 41:43.702
(shallow breathing)

41:50.340 --> 41:51.442
You, too?

42:01.251 --> 42:03.755
Dear God,
I thought you were--
Gather them.

42:03.789 --> 42:06.557
What?
It's started.

42:07.592 --> 42:08.594
It's all right.

42:08.626 --> 42:10.695
I understand.
I'll take care of--
